      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Enrich company profiles with HubSpot and HTTP / REST API at scale for Conversational AI (01789)\n\n**Pattern:** Data Enrichment · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nEnrich company profiles with HubSpot and HTTP / REST API at scale for Conversational AI (01789). It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual conversational ai is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nHourly Schedule → Pull Side A (HubSpot) → Diff the Two Systems → Create Missing in Airtable → Gather Sync Results → Align Field Names → Tag Pipeline Metadata → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to data enrichment without manual effort\n- Anyone automating conversational ai in ai\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n- Responds in seconds\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Airtable PAT; HubSpot private-app token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 900
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
